On most item types, called when the user clicks on a [GUI
item](GUI_items "GUI items") with the mouse.

On [editDefs](EditDef_%28GUI_item_type%29 "EditDef (GUI item type)") ,
this is called when the text changes.

On
[choiceDefs](ChoiceDef_%28GUI_item_type%29 "ChoiceDef (GUI item type)")
, this is called when the selected option changes.

